OL,7,GMembers of the National Union of
OL,8,GJournalists at BBC Northern Ireland are
OL,9,Gvoting in a consultative ballot for
OL,10,Gindustrial action over plans to cut 36
OL,11,Gjobs in the province.
OL,13,FThere's been particular concern about
OL,14,F"disproportionate" staff cuts at BBC
OL,15,FRadio Foyle in Derry-Londonderry, where
OL,16,Feight journalist posts are being
OL,17,Fremoved, resulting in the loss of the
OL,18,Fstation's breakfast show and hourly
OL,19,Fnews bulletins.
OL,3,CBBC Northern Ireland journalists hold
OL,4,Cconsultative ballot for industrial
OL,5,Caction
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G1/9
