PN,35002
SC,0002
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1674394480
OL,7,FEarlier this month, around 250 people
OL,8,Fattended a public meeting in the city
OL,9,Fto voice their opposition to the
OL,10,Fchanges at Radio Foyle.
OL,12,FNegative reaction from the local
OL,13,Fcommunity has featured regularly in the
OL,14,Flocal press since the corporation first
OL,15,Fwent public with its plans in
OL,16,Flate-November.
OL,3,CBBC Northern Ireland journalists hold
OL,4,Cconsultative ballot for industrial
OL,5,Caction
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G2/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35003
SC,0003
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1674394480
OL,7,FNUJ members are said to have been
OL,8,Fangered by the BBC's lack of
OL,9,Fconsultation and its refusal to provide
OL,10,Finformation on the costs of running
OL,11,FRadio Foyle, the potential impact of
OL,12,Fthe cuts on stress, and on equality.
OL,14,FUnion representatives have described
OL,15,Fthe tone of management as
OL,16,F"confrontational and disrespectful
OL,17,Ftowards the union".
OL,3,CBBC Northern Ireland journalists hold
OL,4,Cconsultative ballot for industrial
OL,5,Caction
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G3/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35004
SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1674394480
OL,7,F"The consultative ballot is a response
OL,8,Fto an ill thought out plan which would
OL,9,Fbe bad for journalism, bad for BBC
OL,10,FRadio Foyle and bad for public service
OL,11,Fbroadcasting in Northern Ireland. We
OL,12,Fneed genuine engagement conducted in a
OL,13,Fproper manner and in a spirit of
OL,14,Frespect which frankly has not been
OL,15,Fevident so far. As in England, NUJ
OL,16,Fmembers are anxious to protect the
OL,17,Flocal services and to maximise
OL,18,Femployment. We also need political
OL,19,Fcommitments to protect local radio
OL,20,Facross the UK."
OL,3,CBBC Northern Ireland journalists hold
OL,4,Cconsultative ballot for industrial
OL,5,Caction
