PN,35005
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1674394480
OL,7,FOn Thursday, BBC director-general Tim
OL,8,FDavie appeared before the Public
OL,9,FAccounts Committee at Westminster. The
OL,10,Fdeputy chair of the committee, Geoffrey
OL,11,FClifton-Brown MP, questioned the BBC
OL,12,Fboss on behalf of local MPs Colum
OL,13,FEastwood and Gregory Campbell.
OL,15,F"It is an issue that is felt very
OL,16,Fstrongly locally and it is a long way
OL,17,Ffrom Belfast. It is a very separate
OL,18,Fcommunity out there," said Mr
OL,19,FClifton-Brown.
OL,3,CBBC Northern Ireland journalists hold
OL,4,Cconsultative ballot for industrial
OL,5,Caction
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G5/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35006
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1674394480
OL,7,FHe went on: "...you have 650 staff in
OL,8,FBelfast whereas you only have 20 in
OL,9,FDerry, so it seems a little
OL,10,Fdisproportionate to cut off The
OL,11,FBreakfast Show which a lot of local
OL,12,Fpeople rely on."
OL,14,FMr Davie replied: "...I am going to
OL,15,Fsound a bit like a broken record, but
OL,16,Fwe have to make choices in terms of
OL,17,Fwhere the audience impact is versus
OL,18,Fwhere our money is and where the future
OL,19,Fis going.
OL,3,CBBC Northern Ireland journalists hold
OL,4,Cconsultative ballot for industrial
OL,5,Caction
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G6/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35007
SC,0007
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1674394480
OL,7,F"With regard to Foyle, this is a
OL,8,Fpainful saving, but we believe we
OL,9,Fshould be investing more in digital and
OL,10,Fdoing more across the whole of Northern
OL,11,FIreland in terms of developing the
OL,12,Fproduction sector and other things. We
OL,13,Fthink there are better ways of using
OL,14,Fthe money.
OL,16,F"The Foyle is an opt-out from Radio
OL,17,FUlster. I totally take your point that
OL,18,Fthere are differences in the community
OL,19,Fthere, and they need to be served.
OL,3,CBBC Northern Ireland journalists hold
OL,4,Cconsultative ballot for industrial
OL,5,Caction
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G7/9
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,35008
SC,0008
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F350A1674394480
OL,7,F"What we are protecting ` there will be
OL,8,Fdebate about whether this is enough,
OL,9,Fand clearly many feel it is not ` is
OL,10,Fthree hours of opt during the weekday,
OL,11,Fincluding a full half-an-hour news
OL,12,Fprogramme for that area, which is
OL,13,F137,000 people. We are continuing that.
OL,15,F"We are consulting with our staff to
OL,16,FMay. I note your comments and thank you
OL,17,Ffor raising them."
OL,3,CBBC Northern Ireland journalists hold
OL,4,Cconsultative ballot for industrial
OL,5,Caction
